{"tid":1002974,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"小知識。搭飛機會耳痛既人入黎","createTime":"2019-01-31T10:11:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-25T11:22:03.000Z","uid":111930,"like":18,"dislike":40,"uniUserReply":45,"replies":[{"pid":"87c96ab7fa4fbba41ad5b8effd61cf4f3e573b34","tid":1002974,"uid":111930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T10:11:52.000Z","msg":"純分享。<br />\n就係搭飛機降落隻耳仔會好痛。<br />\n其實有方法解決唔會再咁辛苦<br />\n就係其實部飛機起飛或者係空中果陣你隻耳仔feel到塞塞地既時候，用手禁住兩個鼻lone，唔好有空隙，跟住大大力用鼻噴就會feel到d氣上曬耳仔跟住通曬。咁你係飛機上面一feel到塞就噴一噴，降落時就一dd痛都唔會有。<br />\n要提返，小小塞就要噴一次，積太耐噴既話，噴果下都會痛。<br />\n<br />\n呢個問題我細細坐飛機果陣好困擾，直頭記得幾歲果陣係痛到要喊，但係跟住無意中發現咁樣就會唔痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6f47e4dfff6e95956609d57c6b6fc4636e3303c","tid":1002974,"uid":106523,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T10:13:00.000Z","msg":"潛水會咁做"},{"pid":"1f27f22b1f164f24230e3759844a722c7f30d4b9","tid":1002974,"uid":57513,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T10:13:09.000Z","msg":"打開個口再扮打喊露好似都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a46fb71b6a51a4ec93dac440d4a5baa5069728f5","tid":1002974,"uid":21423,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T10:13:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"54542326fe484f557da4e60e9ea04cdd00dd50fa","tid":1002974,"uid":111930,"like":4,"dislike":5,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"1f27f22b1f164f24230e3759844a722c7f30d4b9","tid":1002974,"uid":57513,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T10:13:09.000Z","msg":"打開個口再扮打喊露好似都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T10:15:53.000Z","msg":"呢個唔得 ，我試過<br />\n可能好多人都得，但係對於降落耳仔會好痛果班人都唔太work"},{"pid":"8d3e7a926ae77c2f4f5edebed7f64680d56e6708","tid":1002974,"uid":57513,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"54542326fe484f557da4e60e9ea04cdd00dd50fa","tid":1002974,"uid":111930,"like":4,"dislike":5,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"1f27f22b1f164f24230e3759844a722c7f30d4b9","tid":1002974,"uid":57513,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T10:13:09.000Z","msg":"打開個口再扮打喊露好似都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T10:15:53.000Z","msg":"呢個唔得 ，我試過<br />\n可能好多人都得，但係對於降落耳仔會好痛果班人都唔太work"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T10:18:05.000Z","msg":"可能人人唔同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我感覺上好似可以打開耳仔某個洞口咁就無事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c04f7c2b95fea86189be3376c77c29c6405b7ab","tid":1002974,"uid":11695,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T10:20:05.000Z","msg":"雖然細個已經知<br />\n仲以為得我會咁做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f9590125664c82157e46f4f077a12f7333d8874","tid":1002974,"uid":130950,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T10:20:07.000Z","msg":"已經做到唔洗禁住個鼻都做到氣壓平衡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ab7fe507c1d15be77db264f079c84f133e1ec9d","tid":1002974,"uid":130901,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T10:21:33.000Z","msg":"有方法完全通晒，但講比十個聽 十個都做唔到"},{"pid":"1476dbf120b86f000bcbe8c6b5474040371071d7","tid":1002974,"uid":17420,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T10:22:07.000Z","msg":"多謝你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53ca9b6262d19f3728641588deccf762b90a4245","tid":1002974,"uid":29093,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T10:23:19.000Z","msg":"常識嚟 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4aa4679d2d1c1d184bfe6d57306b8eb45e7e796d","tid":1002974,"uid":144529,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T10:25:42.000Z","msg":"係常識黎，但樓主靠自己發現到都幾勁"},{"pid":"4ca5b0246dfe50ad5190ca5d37236884bb6a53c5","tid":1002974,"uid":56223,"lik